    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tables with a top, usually round, supported on legs which socket directly into the top; such tables have three legs braced by stretchers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
